94
00:11:37,019 --> 00:11:40,379
[SPEAKER_00] And now we need to go for fiscal consolidation.

95
00:11:40,379 --> 00:11:46,220
[SPEAKER_00] We have to say enough of this sugar rush, we have to do it differently.

96
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:52,379
[SPEAKER_00] While at the same time there are more pressures for defense, more pressures from climate, more

97
00:11:52,379 --> 00:11:53,980
