108
00:12:45,419 --> 00:12:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] And for the Western Balkans, even more, by 9%.

109
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] Just imagine what you can do if you have that much more in terms of GDP.

110
00:12:57,019 --> 00:13:05,500
