111
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] around the investment climate, around the governance performance.

112
00:13:12,059 --> 00:13:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] And the third priority, last on my list, but definitely not least, work together.

113
00:13:20,779 --> 00:13:28,620
