135
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] I also would put a word to Europe to think about the value of the collective.

136
00:16:35,899 --> 00:16:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] And I would argue that the EU budget can lend more of a hand to Europe's transformation.

137
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:53,100
[SPEAKER_00] I know this is not an easy conversation, but at this time it is a paramount decision to be made,

138
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] to have that capacity to lift up Europe's potential.

139
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] So let me conclude in the following way.

140
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:14,619
