142
00:17:21,819 --> 00:17:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] This is one of these moments.

143
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] And I so strongly believe that this region, and more broadly Europe,

144
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:43,500
